    "description": "<strong><i>Luckie Ball</i> is a short precision platformer where nothing is fully solid.</strong> You'll float to the top of everything!<br><br>Inspired by the Flash games you used to play in the school computer lab, <i>Luckie Ball</i> features dozens of hand-drawn levels for you to traverse through. The tight and responsive controls lend well to advanced mechanics and optimized movement.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Collect Luckie Coins to unlock a wealth of bonus levels and character skins!<br></li><li> Take on the Extreme Gauntlet, a set of three torturous levels that'll test the limits of your patience and skill. Expert understanding of the physics engine is mandatory. <br></li><li> Flex your creative muscles with the custom level creator! Share the level file with your friends so they can enjoy your masterpieces too.<br></li><li> Need another way to compete? Set the fastest time you can in Speedrun Mode!</li></ul><br>All of this content is totally free. There's no in-app purchases or paid DLC! That means there's no excuse for you not to play. Or maybe there is. I'm not you, I wouldn't know.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373810/extras/7668b2ac27cde1e5080aa9e69a21639e.poster.avif?t=1681448511\" width=198 height=66 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373810/extras/7668b2ac27cde1e5080aa9e69a21639e.webm?t=1681448511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373810/extras/7668b2ac27cde1e5080aa9e69a21639e.mp4?t=1681448511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
